item.title: Desert Code Camp 2017
item.description: Desert Code Camp 2017 was yesterday. I was slated to give four presentations yesterday. I ended up giving three. Three of them were on F#. I did Introduction to F# in the morning and had two more ready to go in the evening. But by that time everyone in the morning had already gone home, I’m guessing, and so the evening attendees probably would have enjoyed hearing Introduction to F# again!
